𝗗𝗮𝘆 𝟯𝟱: 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗲 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗧𝗲𝗮𝗺, 𝗗𝗼𝗻’𝘁 𝗟𝗲𝗮𝗱 𝗧𝗵𝗲𝗺!
👥 A Scrum Master is a true leader, not a boss!  
👉 Tip: Focus on serving your team’s needs. Empower them to lead while you remove roadblocks.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How often do you serve your team’s needs rather than lead from the front?"  
1. Always a true leader 👥  
2. Most of the time 🤝  
3. Sometimes 🔧  
4. I tend to lead more 🙈
